org.mapstruct.ap.internal.util

Class MapperConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mapstruct.ap.internal.util.MapperConfiguration

  • public class MapperConfiguration
extends Object
    Provides an aggregated view to the settings given via Mapper and MapperConfig for a specific mapper class.

    Settings given via Mapper will generally take precedence over settings inherited from a referenced config class. The lists of referenced mappers given via Mapper.uses() and MapperConfig.uses() will be merged.

    Author:
    Sjaak Derksen
